{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0ab66cbc4","title":"给续范亭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"35772197fb","index":0,"year":1947,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"c0ab66cbc4"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b7c521cc4","name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d0177377d2","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c0ab66cbc4"},{"id":"0c725c9bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年7月13日）范亭同志迁入普绥后，未知贵善如何，极以为念。人民战争发展，极限苦时期虽尚未完，但展望是好的。我们在此都好。我身体比在延安时要好些。敬祝安好！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c0ab66cbc4"},{"id":"0f7dcf959e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c0ab66cbc4"},{"id":"615f0bee8e","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年七月十三日[1]续范亭（1893-1947），山西省峰县（今原平市）西社村人，著名爱间，后与共产党人合作创建山西新军。1947年病查后被递认为中国共产党正式党员。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c0ab66cbc4"}],"page":{"id":"67a71199ca","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"c0ab66cbc4","start":135,"end":135}}}},"__N_SSG":true}